      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i know i should reach out but it just feels so pointless. like even if i talk to someone it doesn't change the fact that i'm just stuck in this loop. honestly sometimes i think the only way to actually get peace is to just make it over. like, what's the point of even trying to 'climb' when the only way to get to the top is to stop forever?",
